Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.36,0:00:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是發生在某個炎熟的夏天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.01,0:00:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.11,0:00:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.55,0:00:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先生怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.92,0:00:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.56,0:01:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請 請 請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.56,0:01:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 麻煩您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.50,0:01:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然接到通知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.50,0:01:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟部長一起\r陪客戶去打高爾夫的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.21,0:01:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老公開的車出了車禍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.58,0:01:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好沒有乘客死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.52,0:01:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造成部長輕傷\r以及我老公跟客户住院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.83,0:01:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.03,0:01:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我現在馬上過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.54,0:02:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(替老公還債的的人妻)\r(情趣玩具逼迫的奴隸生活)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.84,0:02:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.23,0:02:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.13,0:02:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.43,0:02:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.44,0:02:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.84,0:02:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.34,0:03:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.28,0:03:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐木的太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.61,0:03:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.79,0:03:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.26,0:03:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老公給您帶來了極大的困擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.86,0:03:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.86,0:03:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把頭抬起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.50,0:03:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.13,0:03:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常的抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.74,0:03:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別 別這樣 太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.54,0:03:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦 請把頭抬起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.04,0:03:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.15,0:03:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實在的 很不想看到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.29,0:03:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是這個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.46,0:03:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.26,0:03:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說些什麼好这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.90,0:04:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.64,0:04:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您身豐的狀況如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.28,0:04:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體已經沒什麼大礙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.48,0:04:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.25,0:04:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.02,0:04:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.62,0:04:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你了解嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.89,0:04:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.56,0:04:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.47,0:04:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上 那個應酬是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.17,0:04:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙方公司都不知道的應酬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.31,0:04:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受了這次車禍的影響\r對方公司的高層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.48,0:04:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也知道了這次的應酬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.15,0:04:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.52,0:04:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因這次的影響\r我受了降薪跟禁入公司的處分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.27,0:05:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.31,0:05:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太 你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.12,0:05:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道歉的姿勢很迷人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.56,0:05:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個很棒的太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.03,0:05:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼形容好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.30,0:05:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便宜了佐佐木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.34,0:05:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你請回吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.94,0:05:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.78,0:05:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.42,0:05:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.92,0:05:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道該如何彌補
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.15,0:05:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.72,0:06:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不來道歉又不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.16,0:06:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有我做得到的我什麼都做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.33,0:06:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請尽量提出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.27,0:06:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.84,0:06:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都可以提出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.88,0:06:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.28,0:06:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必原諒我先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.65,0:06:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.82,0:06:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.96,0:06:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何事 你都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.46,0:06:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願意為我做嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.67,0:06:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.97,0:06:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.48,0:06:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.51,0:06:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不要緊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.48,0:07:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體還是會常常麻麻的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.06,0:07:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼需要我幫忙的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.99,0:07:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.33,0:07:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.27,0:07:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以當我的手跟腳嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.01,0:07:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您從醫院回來之後\r我一定會來照顧您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 這樣就很幫忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.05,0:07:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以補價我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.77,0:07:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.33,0:07:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你說的彌補啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.01,0:08:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛不是說過了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.88,0:08:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都願意做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.45,0:08:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.92,0:08:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.35,0:08:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.75,0:08:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是願意當我的手跟腳嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.56,0:08:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說\r你願意帮助我做任何事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.16,0:08:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼不一樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.84,0:08:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是佐佐木的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.81,0:08:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我變成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.18,0:08:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.41,0:08:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-可是 -你要像剛剛一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.02,0:08:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都願意做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.09,0:08:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.42,0:08:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個脫掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.86,0:08:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也包含在裡面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.77,0:09:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太你要好好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.13,0:09:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補償我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.17,0:09:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.97,0:10:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.78,0:10:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.65,0:10:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太 你好性感喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.08,0:10:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想幹你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.39,0:10:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.05,0:10:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.10,0:10:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.47,0:10:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.74,0:10:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不可以呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.71,0:10:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我摸嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.94,0:10:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事我做不來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.32,0:11:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放開我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.57,0:11:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還真的不行耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.14,0:11:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我不介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.64,0:11:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以\r不可以這樣請不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.15,0:12:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會很溫柔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.26,0:12:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換個姿勢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.53,0:12:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂轉過來這邊\r我看 還是先那邊好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊要鋪墊子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.04,0:12:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會皺掉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.16,0:12:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經濕了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.86,0:12:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.73,0:12:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 不可以 不可以這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.49,0:13:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 不可以 我想舔那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.64,0:13:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是個好太太耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.44,0:13:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對佐佐木來說太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.28,0:14:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我幹你嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.42,0:14:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.12,0:14:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱情跟愛慕的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.83,0:14:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.36,0:15:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我定會讓你感受到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.96,0:15:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.36,0:16:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要不要親啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.76,0:16:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣\r請別這樣真的別這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.51,0:16:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 不可以這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.21,0:16:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.62,0:17:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你這麼敏感喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.91,0:18:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡一定很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.61,0:18:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.21,0:18:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 不可以看啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.60,0:21:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躺著比較舒服吧\r太太 快點 快點躺下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.15,0:22:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳跨過來比較舒服吧\r跨過去一點 我要舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.39,0:22:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再舔了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.66,0:22:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.30,0:22:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.77,0:22:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.40,0:22:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再舔了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.83,0:23:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-太太 我要\r-不可以 不可以戳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.80,0:23:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不可以戳嗎\r-不可以 我會受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.31,0:23:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.21,0:23:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以截那裹啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.35,0:23:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太 我戳你就動\r不戳到你爽怎麼行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.35,0:23:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 不可以戳那裹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.99,0:23:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏不可以戳啦\r戳了會很敏感 不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.59,0:24:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好濕喔 濕答答的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.45,0:25:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濕答答 滋潤潤的 好舒服喔
